<% content_for :feature do %>
<div class="featured-event">
  <div class="screen-blk">
    <div class="row">
      <h2>Featured event:</h2>
      <div class="row">
        <% if @featured_event %>
          <div class="small-12 columns">
            <h3><a href="<%= @featured_event.url %>" title="<%=@featured_event.title %>"><%= @featured_event.title %></a></h3>
            <!-- <div class="feature-descript"><%= first_p(@featured_event.description).html_safe %></div> -->
          </div>
        <% else %>
          <div class="small-12 columns">
            <h3>No current upcoming event. Check back soon!</h3>
            <!--
            <div class="feature-descript">
              <p>Chances are we just haven't put the next events on the schedule yet. Check back soon to see what's next!</p>
            </div>
            -->
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<% end %>

<div class="row">
  <div class="small-4 columns">
    <h2>Who we are</h2>
    <p>We are a group of individuals who have a common interest in web and software development.</p>
    <p>Our skill levels vary greatly, from complete beginners to seasoned veterans, we welcome anyone with a curiosity for programming.</p>
    <p>We strictly enforce a <%= link_to "Code of Conduct", conduct_path %> to provide all of our members a safe and inclusive environment.</p>
    <p><strong>We aim to educate, empower and connect developers in the Wichita area.</strong></p>
  </div>

  <div class="small-4 columns">
    <h2>What we do</h2>
    <p>Members of devICT have one common goal: to be better at what we do. Our events and services are aimed at achieving that.</p>
    <p>To make that happen we have monthly events that are both social and educational.</p>
    <p>If you visit the <a href="/videos" title="Previous Dev Talks">Videos</a> page, you can see recordings of <a href="/videos" title="Previous Dev Talks">previously given talks</a>.</p>
    <p><a class="button large primary" href="/events" title="Events">View all of our events</a></p>
  </div>

  <div class="small-4 columns">
    <h2>Get involved!</h2>
    <p>Most of the time we are hanging out in <a href="https://devict.slack.com" title="devICT Slack">Slack</a>. To join, just <a href="https://devict-slackin.herokuapp.com/" title="devICT Slack Registration">fill out this form</a>.</p>
    <p>Primarily, be sure to <a href="http://www.meetup.com/devict" title="devICT on Meetup">become a member on the Meetup page</a>. Then you will receive notifications for all coming events.</p>
    <p>You could also give a talk! Share the knowledge, we enjoy learning about any development related topics.</p>
    <p><a href="https://devict-slackin.herokuapp.com/" title="devICT Slack Registration" class="button primary large">Come hang out with us in Slack</a>!</p>
  </div>
</div>
